extendedInfo.description: It has never been easier to stay up to date with the latest career opportunities at Cummins Inc. With the Cummins Careers application, you will have access to our interactive 3D engines section, global job locator, custom feed-based job system and much more - all in the palm of your hand. LEARN: Have you ever wanted to see the inner workings of a Cummins engine? Check out our interactive engines section. Here you will be able to go inside the engine, view various components, find out how they work and see relevant job opportunities. CUSTOM JOB SEARCHES: Customize your job search experience with our unique job feeds section. Here you can save feeds based on areas or locations of interest. You can also save your favorites and email positions to yourself to apply to once youâre on a desktop. STAY INFORMED: Get videos from the Cummins Careers YouTube channel and stay up to date with the latest news from the Cummins recruiting team via our news feed. FEATURES: â¢Interactive 3D engines section â¢Custom job feeds and keyword searches â¢Global jobs map for browsing job listings by location â¢Save favorite jobs for easy access later â¢Share jobs with friends â¢Cummins history timeline â¢Cummins TV section with videos from the Cummins Careers YouTube channel â¢About Cummins section with info on our sustainability and diversity initiatives â¢News feed with updates from the Cummins recruiting team
